Prerequisites
=============
Before proceding, you have to make sure you have installed and configured
all prerequisite packages.

Globus
------

Building StoRM gridftp-dsi
==========================
./bootstrap

./configure --with-globus-nothr-flavor=<globus-flavor> --with-globus-prefix=<globus-location> --prefix=<prefix>

make; make install; make rpm

